(76706, -1, 'setting_as_refresh_desc', 'vbsettings', 'This setting controls how often the activity stream is auto updated with new activity while the user is viewing the stream.  The default is every one minute. If the user leaves the page unattended, the auto update will be suspended after 5 minutes. If you set this option to greater than 5 minutes, the refresh will be suspended after the first refresh if the page is unattended.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1336800751, '4.2.0 Alpha 1', 0),
