(76968, -1, 'setting_forumhomedepth_desc', 'vbsettings', 'Depth to show forums on forum home forum listings. If you set this value to ''2'', forum listings will show the current forum level and any child forums one level below (etc.)', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1199365736, '3.7.0 Beta 4', 0),
