(76972, -1, 'setting_friendlyurl_canonical_desc', 'vbsettings', 'This options defines how canonical URLs are enforced for guest users (including search engines).<br /><br />\r\n\r\nIf <em>Standard</em> is selected then guest users will be redirected to the correct URL if they request a page using the wrong <em>Friendly URL</em> format.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nIf <em>Strict</em> is selected then guest users will also be redirected to the correct URL if they request a page using the wrong text.  This may also include requesting URLs in the wrong character set.', 'vbulletin', 'vBulletin Solutions', 1266600552, '4.0.3', 0),
