(41, 83, 'Ka_Khan', 'Re: Test', 'Dear Abbas,\r\nSalams.\r\nHope you and your family is fine.The other day you called but i was away.Then i called you number and it was busy.The same ''musical chair'' we have :)\r\nTrying to make the forum active.But it seems new Mods and exhausted.Denovo is out of scene.12 Guage is following his own track.Vik tries to fill the gaps but most of his threads are of low quality.Starfish is good.\r\nHave added the ''Mods threads'' and also ''Visiting old threads'' in the Oxygen Spa.Just guide me what else we could do.\r\nMost of our scenior and old members are busy with life.I will suggest a mail sent to them wishing them good health and telling them we are missing our brothers.\r\nWas thinking of calling you last night but again it was too late when i came home.Will try to call you today.\r\nRegards,\r\nKamran', 'a:1:{s:2:"cc";a:1:{i:1;s:5:"Abbas";}}', 0, 1296406218, 1, 1, 0, 0),
