(44, 1, 'Abbas', 'Re: Test', 'Salams Kamran,\n\nHope you''re doing well, sorry for not being able to get in touch. Have been traveling all over and sadly till yesterday not even getting a chance to fire my new Taurus 709 Slim! :|\n\nIt''s good that you are in touch with mods and guiding them, Vik needs some more guidance as he is a little blunt with members [url]http://www.pakguns.com/showthread.php?5275-Best-CC-9mm-Pistol&p=172959#post172959[/url] (Post 27), also with low quality content. What is with Karachi mods ? ;(\n\nTaurus is in Dubai, he seems to be going though a rough patch with his domestic life. I talked to him a few days back, he was telling me he might be getting a divorce. Bhabhi is also acting very unlady like by calling any senior PakGuns members Saleem was friends with and telling him foolish stories like Saleem being on the run from Pakistan with multiple FIR''s against him, him having stolen 25 million of her father''s money and taking all her jewelery and stuff. At first I was shocked on hearing the same story from multiple people calling me but then all told me they had received a call from Bhabhi. Anyway talked to Taurus and all is well on his end, the stories are all crap.\n\nHope the new 9mm ammo comes to the market soon, prices are touching Rs. 40-45 here in Lahore.', 'a:1:{s:2:"cc";a:1:{i:83;s:7:"Ka_Khan";}}', 0, 1297055772, 1, 1, 0, 0),
