(46, 12, 45, 'Abbas', 1, '', 1230409545, 'Hi Muzzogr8. Welcome to Pak Guns !\n\nI''m sorry I can''t really help you with the Karachi info as I live in Lahore but I remember reading somewhere that Karsaz may offer the facility.\n\nAs far as getting a decent weapon. First you have the get a FireArm license made (approximate guide on how to get one on the main webpage). Once that''s done, we''ll guide you to the best possible firearm purchase.', 0, 1, '117.102.5.174', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 14, 49),
