(148, 6, 15, 'Abbas', 1, '', 1230907301, 'All of you guys have good suggestions, I like your contribution of testing firing the new Glocks the best Cap1 ;)\n\nThe bumper stickers and the T-shirts are a good idea for the first phase. I''ll get on it from next week.  As far as the member subscription thing perhaps we can do it at a later stage, I can bear the costs for the time being as I want it to be a free for all. Our Gun Enthusiasts friends deserve access to good free Pakistan relevant information and InshAllah together all of us will be able to provide it.\n\nAs far as the lobbying for change in Gun laws, well that''s going to happen over quite a bit of time and mostly by uniting everyone''s contacts rather than money. Money will mostly be required for ad''s in papers, but that''s a plan for another day :)\n\nFiring ranges already exist in all major cities but they are exclusive access only. It''s going to take some time and work but as we grow in size we can work out a cost effective deal with some of them for PakGuns members.', 0, 1, '117.102.5.174', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 7, 157),
