(157, 1, 1, 'OHQ', 25, '', 1230965679, 'Sallam to all...............................\n\nMy name is Omar Hamza Qureshi from Murree. Love arms very much. I was thinking why there is no Pakistani website on arms. Now there is thanks to abbas bhahi. Good work keep it up. I don’t know if you remember me abbas bhahi from pakistani tech forum. I own a CF-98 don’t have much information about guns but sure will have soon thanks to you abbas bhahi.', 0, 1, '115.186.96.124', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 2, 172),
