(161, 27, 0, 'Firepower!', 16, '', 1230968037, 'I am a big fan of .45 caliber. I carry Glock 21 in this caliber. I chose it over HK USP for its durabilty and the well know torture test it went through, successfully. \n[url]http://theprepared.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=90&Itemid=40[/url]\n\nIn addition, you can really find lots of accessories for Glock such as FSSG, Stock, Safety lever, internal laser, M3 combo, night sights, etc.\n[url]http://www.tactical-life.com/online/wp-content/uploads/2008/01/glock21.jpg[/url]\n\nI would like to know what do you guys prefer in .45 and why?', 0, 1, '58.27.163.244', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 33, 176),
