(163, 19, 106, 'Firepower!', 16, '', 1230968802, '300 Win. Mag. can actaully out preform 30.06 and 7mm Mag when hitting beyond certain distance. Also I pack much more punch and velocity than 30.06. For example: \n\n200 gr Bullet \n30.06 Sprng Muzzle Velocity of 2543 and energy of  2873 at 500 yards MV is 1417 and Energy is 892\n300Win Mag Muzzle Velocity of 2930 and energy of 3810 at 500 yards MV is 2030 and Energy is 1840', 0, 1, '58.27.163.244', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 23, 178),
