(270, 7, 24, 'Abbas', 1, '', 1231248661, 'Actually I think they are well trained and pretty much everyone there knows the procedure for the transportation of weapons. Even at the most paranoid Isb airport, I once forgot to tell them before hand about the weapon. They put my bag though the scanner and asked who''s bag is this, without announcing there was a gun in it. I told them it was mine, they asked for my license and pretty much followed procedure from there. I forgot to add in the original post that it''s recommended that the magazines be empty and the bullets transported in their own box.\n\nA lot of people carry weapons between cities nowadays so it has more or less become a norm for the airport staff.', 0, 1, '117.102.5.174', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 8, 336),
