(297, 18, 105, 'Abbas', 1, '', 1231275644, '15,000 + easy for the 24/7, Cougar and the PT92/99.\n\nOfcourse 99 % of people wouldn''t put anything even remotely close to 15,000 rounds though it (average is 300 in the entire service life of the pistol). Btw 15 k rounds would cost Rs. 40 x 15,000 = Rs. 600,000. So I''m sure a person who can fire 6 lakh ruppes worth of ammo isn''t going to worry about a Rs. 10 k barrel.\n\n>I misread the question above and edited my post according.', 0, 1, '117.102.5.174', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 22, 378),
