(488, 60, 0, 'Omkhan', 47, '', 1231502270, 'Hi all, \n\nJust want to know how many ppl here carry their weapons with them. & In what condition the fire arm is carried. What do u guys do when 144 is imposed & u dont have the permit for it? \n\nBTW, if 144 is not in place. one can legally carry his/her firearm along with its license  with them in a concealed manner. \n\nFor me, when 144 is not in place, I carry often. My CF 98 goes with me most of the time with 1 bullet in the chamber, hammer down & safety off. Since the DA pull of it is quite long so I feel safe carrying it in this condition.  My 2 mags hold 13 rounds each.  When its 144, I do abide the law, however, I think I need to get the 144 permit so that I dont have to keep check of 144. \n\nSo what do u guys do & in what manner?', 0, 1, '221.132.113.98', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 84, 654),
