(529, 41, 262, 'Acciprone', 20, '', 1231566778, 'Hi All \n\nI have been dealing with Haris Traders for last few months they have some of the best stuff in Karachi and also of very high repute. The only problem is that if they dont know you the stuff is a little expensive . If you deal with them on a regular basis then they warm up to you and give you good deals. But the stuff they give you is genuine and of high quality. They do carry revolvers but these days due to the situation they do not have any fresh stock. I will be going today and i can check and post back. Last i visited them I was intrested in a .357 saw one with a 6 inch barrel for about 90, which i thought was expensive. \n\nRgds', 0, 1, '203.81.217.245', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 55, 705),
