(549, 64, 538, 'Abbas', 1, '', 1231581718, 'Chinese ammo and POF ammo are about on par with each other accuracy wise. POF are more messy and both have perhaps a 1 in 150 round misfire ratio. The thick dull jackets for the POF & are also a factor in FTE on some pistols, whereas the Chinese ones load and work better in cheap striker fired pistols like the 24/7 series due to shiner jackets and softer primers compared to POF.\n\nRegardless both are fine as sport or SD ammo although I always use American / European ammo. More peace of mind then anything else.', 0, 1, '117.102.5.174', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 88, 725),
