(630, 1, 1, 'Cap1', 6, '', 1231666003, '[quote=Conceal Carry]\nRemember! legally armed, law abiding ctizens not only help in controling / reducing crime rate in the society, they also act as 2nd/ 3rd line of defence an any armed conflict with any adversary of Pakistan.[/quote]\nDefinitely! Thanks for the good sum up on our role. Welcome and (since I hear you went) Hajj Mubarak!!', 0, 1, '202.70.154.115', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 2, 828),
(631, 68, 582, 'Cap1', 6, '', 1231667320, 'I also plan to get a shotgun next month once I get another license. Someone told me not to get a repeater as it is very prone to jams and that pump action is most reliable for self defense.', 0, 1, '202.70.154.115', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 94, 829),
(632, 1, 1, 'Abbas', 1, '', 1231667489, '[quote=Conceal Carry]Assalamualykum everyone, I''m a professional from Karachi and and an avid gun enthusiast. I have been / am a memebr of many gun forums on the net and always felt the need for a pure Pakistani forum for serious Pakistani gun enthusiasts. I''m really glad to see this forum and appreciate the initiative and efforts by Abbas.\n\nGun communities in other countries are very strong and have a good say regarding gun laws in their countries. I''ll request all members to be very carefull in their posts and show that gun community in Pakistan is very decent, sensible, sober and law abiding.\n\nI''ll also request Abbas and the moderators of this forum to be strict on such things and remove posts which use bad/abusive language, racial/religious slurs, or depict an illegitimate/illegal behaviour. I''m sure this forum will be a success and a good place to learn and share knowledge, in the future to come togather we might even start to have shooting competetions, etc.\n\nRemember! legally armed, law abiding ctizens not only help in controling / reducing crime rate in the society, they also act as 2nd/ 3rd line of defence an any armed conflict with any adversary of Pakistan.\n\nLet''s make tis forum a success and a fun place to be...[/quote]\n\n\nWsalams Conceal Carry and Welcome to PakGuns. I read in a post that you were gone for Hajj, MashAllah, that''s a great blessing. \n\nI couldn''t agree with your post more. Our aim is to create a responsible, educated close knit gun community in Pakistan.  \n\nInshAllah I won''t have to moderate anything judging from the quality of our members here. Everyone so far is mature and decent. Rest assured any illegal or abusive behavior will be acted upon swiftly. PakGuns is a good starting point for our club and we won''t let anyone ruin things for the rest of us. InshAllah I have no doubt we''ll graduate to a full fledge club with common benefits like cheaper ammo, firing ranges, shooting competitions, proper training facilities, licensing help and perhaps one day even our own gun dealership to give members discounted prices.\n\nTake care and good to have you with us.', 0, 1, '117.102.5.174', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 2, 830),
(633, 68, 582, 'Abbas', 1, '', 1231668094, 'For self defense I would recommend a pistol grip pump action with a folding stock. Depending on your range (125k to 200 k) the Franchi or the Benelli are good choices. In the 75k to 100k range the FabArm is good and 35 K to 60 K the many Turkish variants (Viper, Akkar, Hatsan, Germinca) are decent. Also have a look at the Maverick which is a cheaper Mossberg for around 45K..', 0, 1, '117.102.5.174', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 94, 831),
(634, 54, 399, 'Abbas', 1, '', 1231668466, 'Perfect thanks.', 0, 1, '117.102.5.174', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 73, 833),
(635, 68, 582, 'Cap1', 6, '', 1231668837, 'Thanks Abbas this is very helpful. I think you mentioned somewhere that some shotguns come with a short barrel for self defense and longer barrel for hunting. Which brands offer this combination?', 0, 1, '202.70.154.115', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 94, 834),
(636, 68, 582, 'Acciprone', 20, '', 1231669251, 'HI Cap1.\n\nTry the germenica. it should cost you about 75 k and it has two barrels one for self defence and the other for hunting. Also try the turkish tomahawk it will cost u about 65k this one also comes with two barrel. If you try at Haris trader you might get these . Also I would very strongly recomend going to baluchistan traders near lucky star, the guy there Aftab Sb, is realiable and well offers good advise. So that might be of help. If you need any help from my end please do let me know \n\nRegards', 0, 1, '203.81.237.84', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 94, 835),
(637, 60, 488, 'Cap1', 6, '', 1231669285, '[quote=acciprone]Guys, \n\nI used to my PT 99 concealed but not any more now i just jeep it my car whe i am out. If 144 is in effect then no carrying arms unless you are with your family , that is also cause they stop your car . Regardless , if the 144 is in effect you cannot carry your gun on you as it is not permitted. You can only keep your gun on your property i.e house/car.[/quote]\n\nThanks I didn''t know you could still keep it in your car even during 144.\n\nWhat exactly does 144 say? From what I saw it seems to prohibit unlawful assembly and being armed in an such assembly. Not sure what this means for some one going alone or with family. Also how do we know when and where 144 is imposed and when it is revoked?', 0, 1, '202.70.154.115', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 84, 836),
(638, 60, 488, 'Acciprone', 20, '', 1231669621, 'Cap 1\n\nWhat i meant was i carry only when i am with my family, even if the 144 is in effect. Cause if you have ladies in the car they dont stop you. 144 means that you are prohibited to carry arms even if u have a licence. As for finding out most news paper will carry a small story saying that 144 is in effect and when it has ended. \n\nIF the 144 is not in effect you could keep your gun on the blooming dashboard and the police couldnt legally do any thing if you have ur licence on you. But over time i have learnt from from friends that keep a loaded gun with the safety on near you groin area or near the hand break if at worst you need to use it. \n\nregards', 0, 1, '203.81.237.84', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 84, 837),
(639, 68, 582, 'Cap1', 6, '', 1231669668, 'Wow thanks acciprone! Will look into these options and let you know if I need help.', 0, 1, '202.70.154.115', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 94, 838),
