(718, 35, 212, 'Bored2676', 13, '', 1231770981, 'Powder solvent and Hoppes gun oil / Rem oil\n\nWD-40 is fine for a while but over a period of time in some imported barrels (if you look at it with a bore snake) it leaves some deposits which usually do not anything but at times also ruin the grooves of the barrel.  So basically, as long as you dont use WD-40 to clean the barrel, it should be fine', 0, 1, '203.82.55.89', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 45, 969),
