(822, 77, 0, 'Omkhan', 47, '', 1231834497, 'Turkish weapons have recently (last 2 years i guess) been introduced here in PK & I found them to have a very good finish than the chinese counterparts. They are also reasonably priced I think. e.g. Tisas from Turkey has some very good guns on its portfolio. I was tempted badly to buy Tisas Kanuni S but let it go for CF98 because it was heavy & a bit larger than CF98. Kanuni S is almost a 92fs copy & has really good finish. It costs around 50K. \n\nThere is also a very neat looking handgun Zigana Sports/T/F by Tisas. Zigana Sports cost around 75K last I checked. Then there is Turkish Garison, Sarsilmaz which I believe ConcealCarry has. Its a clone of CZ. \nhere is the website of Tisas [url]http://www.trabzonsilah.com[/url].\n\nAny one out there own turkish weapons? Kindly post ur experience here. Moreover, Would u prefer Chinese handguns over Turkish ones or not? e.g. CF98/NP42 VS Kanuni S & Norinco NZ-85B VS Sarsilmaz B6 & so on.', 0, 1, '221.132.113.98', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 109, 1142),
