(855, 73, 757, 'Abbas', 1, '', 1231851828, 'I am really impressed with our growth however what''s more satisfying to me is to see everyone benefit from our common hobby. I disliked whenever I heard people and friends go around asking numnuts for gun advice and having to call in favors and paying insane amounts for gun licenses. In PakGuns we now have a platform to gather around to discuss our hobby freely and save quite a bit of money too with our information exchange!\n\nFirearms are every man''s right. InshAllah together we''ll help facilitate that.', 0, 1, '117.102.5.174', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 105, 1198),
