(3226, 204, 0, 'Firepower!', 16, '', 1233923097, 'Do you guys favor a collection and variety of pistols/revolvers or just one expensive and reputed piece. I ask this because recently I have seen a quite a few people loading up on Turkish, Chinese and Brazillian imports. However, they always shy away from Glock, HK, Sig, Beretta etc. Whereas if they would sell half of their abovementioned imports, they could easily get Glock HK etc. \n\nWhat do you think?\n\nI for one like to have a few quality guns, and possibly not more than one from one company. If I do happen to end up with more than one from same company, I try to have them in different calibers, at least.', 0, 1, '58.65.152.225', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 279, 4090),
